How to install:


Move the the content to a folder named "beacon" in the modules folder.

Create an account at http://www.beaconpush.com if you don't already have 
one and find your API key and Secret key (go to your account page).

Apply you API key and Secret key inside the module config file (the only 
file inside the configs folder)

Enable the module in your bootstrap.php file.

Have fun with real-time features!

Documentation can be found if you enable the userguide module that comes 
with Kohana.